ivardefs.name: componentId
ivardefs.desc: The internal component unique identification. This is a provision for manufacture specific standard components using a private OID. 11073-10101 has a partition for private OID semantic that the manufacturer can make use of.

ivardefs.name: productionSpec
ivardefs.desc: The printable string defining the component.

ivardefs.name: specType
ivardefs.desc: The specification type, such as, serial number, part number, hardware revision, software revision, etc.

properties.desc: The production specification such as component revision, serial number, etc.
